      <title>肯尼亚先令创历史新低，在欧洲债券截止日期前面临进一步压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/kenya-shilling-kes-usd-at-record-low-faces-pressure-ahead-of-eurobond-payment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲债券偿还期限之前提供近9亿美元的新融资承诺未能使肯尼亚先令免于跌至新低，分析师预测，随着进口成本上升推高对美元的需求，肯尼亚先令将进一步走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/kenya-shilling-kes-usd-at-record-low-faces-pressure-ahead-of-eurobond-payment</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
