      <title>Evercore ISI 的伊曼纽尔表示，非软着陆目前仍处于搁置状态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-22/non-soft-landing-is-still-on-the-shelf-for-now-emanuel-video</link>
