      <title>尼日尔再次错过债券支付，给该地区的银行带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/niger-misses-another-bond-payment-posing-risk-to-region-s-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于7月军事政变引发的制裁，尼日尔错过了越来越多的债券支付，这可能威胁到西非银行业的金融稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/niger-misses-another-bond-payment-posing-risk-to-region-s-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
